data.description: This beautiful updated South Florida home has a 2023 NEW ROOF, NEW 2022 AC, 2023 Water Filter System for the whole house, for water soften, purification and kills virus, bacteria in water, the system ranges PH 6.5 to 8.0,  2022 PVC fence and the highest rated hurricane impact windows, glass impact front door, garage impact door, impact rear slide door. The garage is insulated to be used as a family storage room, however it can easily be converted back to a garage. The appliances are all high end. Master has a huge walk-in closet!!! The backyard is the biggest in our area,  with a built in large pool. There is also wooden storage shed on the side of the house. The HOA is only $150 A YEAR! Coral Bay is surrounded by shopping centers and restaurants all within a mile radius.
